# React + shadcn/ui Dark Design System

## Design Philosophy
> "Darkness is the design, color is the exception."

Rich charcoal with depth layers — NOT flat pure black. Premium minimalism with near-invisible structure. Color accent limited to ~5% of the UI surface area.

## Color Palette

### Core Tokens (CSS Variables)
```css
:root {
  /* Page background — rich charcoal, NOT pure black */
  --background: 240 6% 6%;           /* #0f0f11 */
  --foreground: 0 0% 98%;            /* #fafafa */

  /* Cards — slightly elevated from background */
  --card: 240 5% 8%;                 /* #131316 */
  --card-foreground: 0 0% 98%;

  /* Popover/Dropdown */
  --popover: 240 5% 10%;             /* #18181b */
  --popover-foreground: 0 0% 98%;

  /* Primary accent — ONLY color in the UI */
  --primary: 210 100% 50%;           /* Project-specific, keep interchangeable */
  --primary-foreground: 0 0% 98%;

  /* Secondary */
  --secondary: 240 4% 16%;           /* #27272a */
  --secondary-foreground: 0 0% 98%;

  /* Muted */
  --muted: 240 4% 16%;
  --muted-foreground: 240 5% 55%;    /* #8b8b94 */

  /* Borders — near invisible */
  --border: 240 4% 14%;              /* rgba(255,255,255,0.08) equivalent */
  --input: 240 4% 14%;
  --ring: var(--primary);

  /* Destructive */
  --destructive: 0 72% 51%;          /* #dc2626 */
  --destructive-foreground: 0 0% 98%;

  /* Radius */
  --radius: 0.5rem;
}
```

### Hex Quick Reference
| Usage | Hex | Description |
|-------|-----|-------------|
| Page bg | `#0f0f11` | Rich charcoal |
| Card bg | `#131316` | Slightly elevated |
| Popover | `#18181b` | Dropdown/modal bg |
| Border | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Near-invisible |
| Text primary | `#fafafa` | High contrast white |
| Text muted | `#8b8b94` | Subdued secondary |
| Text dim | `#52525b` | Hints, timestamps |

## Hard Rules

### DO
- ✅ Rich charcoal backgrounds with subtle depth layers
- ✅ Near-invisible borders (white at 8-10% opacity)
- ✅ Center all content — titles, values, labels
- ✅ Uppercase, small, muted section/widget titles
- ✅ Large prominent values/data
- ✅ Generous spacing (think breathing room)
- ✅ Subtle hover states (`bg-white/5` or `bg-white/[0.03]`)
- ✅ Smooth transitions on all interactive elements
- ✅ Status colors used semantically only (green=active, red=error, amber=loading)

### DON'T
- ❌ Pure black (`#000000`) anywhere
- ❌ Glassmorphism / backdrop-blur
- ❌ Glow effects / colored shadows / box-shadow with color
- ❌ Gradients (unless extremely subtle, background-only)
- ❌ Heavy borders or divider lines
- ❌ Color splashes beyond the 5% accent budget
- ❌ Bright/saturated colors outside of status indicators
- ❌ Default shadcn/ui zinc theme without customization

## Component Patterns

### Card
```tsx
<div className="bg-[#131316] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-lg p-6">
  <h3 className="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground text-center mb-4">
    Widget Title
  </h3>
  <div className="text-center">
    {/* Content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

### Status Indicator
```tsx
// Semantic colors only — green/red/amber for meaning, not decoration
const statusColors = {
  listening: "bg-emerald-500",   // Active/recording
  idle: "bg-zinc-600",           // Inactive
  loading: "bg-amber-500",      // Processing/loading
  error: "bg-red-500",          // Error state
} as const;

<div className="flex items-center gap-2">
  <div className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full ${statusColors[status]} ${status === 'listening' ? 'animate-pulse' : ''}`} />
  <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">
    {status}
  </span>
</div>
```

### Button (Primary)
```tsx
<button className="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
  Action
</button>
```

### Button (Ghost/Secondary)
```tsx
<button className="hover:bg-white/[0.05] text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm transition-colors">
  Secondary
</button>
```

### Dropdown/Select
```tsx
<select className="bg-[#18181b] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm text-foreground focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none">
  <option>Option</option>
</select>
```

### Progress Bar
```tsx
<div className="w-full h-1.5 bg-white/[0.05] rounded-full overflow-hidden">
  <div
    className="h-full bg-primary rounded-full transition-all duration-300"
    style={{ width: `${percent}%` }}
  />
</div>
```

### Scrollable Text Area (Transcript)
```tsx
<div className="bg-[#0a0a0c] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-lg p-4 h-64 overflow-y-auto font-mono text-sm text-foreground/90 leading-relaxed">
  {transcript}
</div>
```

## Layout Principles

### Window Layout
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Window chrome (Tauri titlebar)         │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                         │
│     p-6 outer padding                   │
│                                         │
│     ┌─────────────────────────────┐     │
│     │  Content centered, max-w    │     │
│     │  gap-4 between sections     │     │
│     └─────────────────────────────┘     │
│                                         │
│     Generous vertical spacing           │
│                                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Spacing Scale
- Between major sections: `gap-6` or `space-y-6`
- Between related items: `gap-3` or `space-y-3`
- Inner padding on cards: `p-5` or `p-6`
- Window padding: `p-6`

## Typography
- **Titles/Labels:** `text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground`
- **Values/Data:** `text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground` (make data prominent)
- **Body text:** `text-sm text-foreground/90`
- **Hints:** `text-xs text-zinc-500`
- **Monospace (transcript):** `font-mono text-sm`

## Animations
```css
/* Pulse for active recording indicator */
@keyframes pulse-subtle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; }
}

/* Use Tailwind's built-in */
.animate-pulse { /* for status dots */ }

/* Smooth transitions on everything interactive */
transition-colors duration-150
transition-all duration-200
```

## Tailwind Config Extensions
```ts
// tailwind.config.ts
export default {
  darkMode: "class",
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        background: "hsl(var(--background))",
        foreground: "hsl(var(--foreground))",
        card: "hsl(var(--card))",
        primary: "hsl(var(--primary))",
        muted: {
          DEFAULT: "hsl(var(--muted))",
          foreground: "hsl(var(--muted-foreground))",
        },
      },
      borderColor: {
        DEFAULT: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)",
      },
    },
  },
}
```

## Anti-Patterns to Reject
```tsx
// ❌ REJECT: Pure black backgrounds
<div className="bg-black">

// ❌ REJECT: Glassmorphism
<div className="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/10">

// ❌ REJECT: Glow effects
<div className="shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">

// ❌ REJECT: Gradient backgrounds
<div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500">

// ❌ REJECT: Heavy borders
<div className="border-2 border-zinc-500">

// ❌ REJECT: Left-aligned titles (center everything)
<h2 className="text-left">Title</h2>

// ✅ CORRECT: Rich charcoal + near-invisible border
<div className="bg-[#131316] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-lg">

// ✅ CORRECT: Centered muted title
<h2 className="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground text-center">
```
